reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars FORMAT on intended device 1st! Works good!
reviews.reviewText: I've transferred multiple files, large files, file transfers starting at different times, and everything transferred smoothly. Transfers between 5 to 10 mps so far, I haven't added more then 10 gigs yet.Amazon fire TV requires this to be formatted, so before you go load it up, format this on the intended device you plan on using it on otherwise you'll have to transfer everything again. ENJOY!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great look and price
reviews.reviewText: This is such a cool looking USB drive on top of being a good price. Fits on a key ring and is weather resistant. I liked it so much that I bought a second one.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars It is not working
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this flash drive to backup files on my computer. The 256GB capacity would backup a lot of files,I plugged it into my Mac computer and it showed up on the screen with the capacity it should have. So I started the slow process of transferring files from my computer hard drive to the flash drive. Everything worked great until I reached about 20-30 GBs of files on the flash drive I got an error stating the files could not be copied to the location. When I opened File Manager, the flash drive was no longer listed. I rebooted the system but the flash drive is not any more recognized.
